    <h1 class="pf-name">Tyrannosaurus Rex</h1>
    <p class="pf-essence">You were built to move first, and the hardest thing you will ever learn is when not to.</p>
    <div class="pf-tags">
      <span class="pf-tag"><span class="k">Symbolic element</span> Fire</span>
      <span class="pf-tag"><span class="k">Western</span> Aries</span>
      <span class="pf-tag"><span class="k">Chinese</span> Dragon</span>
    </div>
    <div class="pf-actions">
      <a class="btn" href="/vs.html?with=tyrannosaurus-rex">Challenge a friend</a>
      <button class="btn ghost" id="pfShare" type="button">Share this animal</button>
